node.text: Ever wondered how to make COCONUT WHIPPED CREAM🤔? The struggle can be real, but we’re showing you our foolproof methods for PERFECT coconut whip every time😋! We share tips, tricks, and detail exactly what coconut cream brands will set you up for success🥥🥛. Read our STEP-BY-STEP methods via the LINK in our bio! #howto #whippedcream #plantbased #dessert⁠

node.title: How To Make Coconut Whipped Cream

node.text:
It's officially pumpkin season 🎃, and what better way to welcome it with a DIY Pumpkin Pie Spice? 🍂 Our homemade blend is simple, flavor-PACKED, and ready for allll your pies 🥧, lattes ☕️, baked oats, and MORE! 🍁🎃⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Find the recipe here: minimalistbaker.com/diy-pumpkin-pie-spice/⁠⁠
⁠⁠
#pumpkinspice #pumpkinspiceseason #pumpkinpie #pumpkinrecipes #fallrecipes

🥥 Featured Recipe of the Week 🥥 Super Chunky Coconut Granola! This granola is clustery, DREAMY, oh-so-wholesome, and ready for all your smoothie bowls 🍌, fresh almond milk 🥛, and snack packs. 😍 Who's ready to make some?⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Find the recipe here: minimalistbaker.com/super-chunky-coconut-granola/⁠⁠
⁠⁠
#granola #vegangranola #veganbreakfast #granolarecipe #homemadegranola

Looking for an EASY dinner this week? Try our Curried Sweet Potato 🍠 & Chickpea Sheet Pan meal! It's perfectly curry-spiced, full of plant-based nutrients 🌿, and requires just 15 minutes prep time! 🙌🏻 Get your sheet pans ready and make this tonight!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Find the recipe here: minimalistbaker.com/sheet-pan-meal-curried-sweet-potato-chickpeas/⁠⁠
⁠⁠
#vegandinner #vegandinnerideas #easyveganrecipes #healthyrecipes

Our GF Banana Bread is a 1-bowl WONDER you need to try! 🍌🍞 We know you've all got a few ripe bananas hanging around the kitchen 😉...use them up in this EASY, scrumptious recipe that's perfect for prepping for grab-and-go breakfasts or as a sweet snack or dessert anytime of day!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Find the recipe here: minimalistbaker.com/one-bowl-gluten-free-banana-bread/⁠⁠
⁠⁠
#bananabread #veganbananabread  #glutenfreebaking #veganbaking #glutenfreebreakfast

#applerecipes #apples #fallrecipes #veganrecipes
